00:16:10,900 --> 00:16:13,030
I'll try calling his cell again.

285
00:16:13,040 --> 00:16:15,550
If you see him, could you please
let him know for me as well?

286
00:16:15,900 --> 00:16:17,320
Yeah, got it.

287
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:29,800
Just don't go accidentally making
any promises about the future and getting yourself trapped.

288
00:16:31,990 --> 00:16:35,830
Why did I end up
doing what my brother said, anyway?

289
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,000
Still...

290
00:16:42,290 --> 00:16:45,040
Work experience with Tojo, huh?

291
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:51,250
With Tojo.

292
00:16:51,740 --> 00:16:52,940
Spending time together...

293
00:16:53,200 --> 00:16:55,510
for work experience.

294
00:16:55,970 --> 00:16:56,970
With Tojo.

295
00:16:57,010 --> 00:16:58,210
Together.

296
00:17:11,490 --> 00:17:13,560
Go get me two cartons of milk.

297
00:17:14,370 --> 00:17:15,580
What a pain.

298
00:17:26,450 --> 00:17:27,950
Come on, please?

299
00:17:37,810 --> 00:17:38,810
And so...

300
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:43,200
Ah...

301
00:17:43,540 --> 00:17:44,740
This convenience store...

302
00:17:45,590 --> 00:17:46,950
is the one where I did my high school

303
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:49,650
work experience.

304
00:17:52,190 --> 00:17:53,690
That's 184 yen.

305
00:17:56,980 --> 00:17:58,470
417 yen.

306
00:17:58,760 --> 00:18:02,260
- Would you like this meal heated up?
- Yes, please.

307
00:18:02,860 --> 00:18:05,400
All right, one moment, please.

308
00:18:11,830 --> 00:18:13,260
Brings back memories.

309
00:18:15,450 --> 00:18:17,680
I need milk anyway, so I might as well get it here.

310
00:18:33,280 --> 00:18:34,380
Welcome.

311
00:18:34,900 --> 00:18:35,900
Huh?

312
00:18:38,480 --> 00:18:42,300
This guy is Ayato's classmate... Hatano.

313
00:18:46,010 --> 00:18:47,210
I knew it.

314
00:18:48,650 --> 00:18:50,570
I can't give up on you.

315
00:18:53,090 --> 00:18:56,090
You... what are you doing here?

316
00:18:57,420 --> 00:18:58,510
Oh, no.

317
00:18:59,000 --> 00:19:01,230
This is really, really bad.

318
00:19:03,580 --> 00:19:06,500
You... what are you doing here?

319
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:10,700
Oh, uh, no.

320
00:19:11,610 --> 00:19:13,950
I used to do my work experience here.

321
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:15,000
Huh?

322
00:19:15,080 --> 00:19:16,280
You did?

323
00:19:17,080 --> 00:19:18,950
I'm doing my work experience here right now.

324
00:19:19,110 --> 00:19:19,980
What?

325
00:19:20,780 --> 00:19:21,980
What a coincidence.

326
00:19:22,590 --> 00:19:25,480
I can't believe that while I was lost in nostalgia,

327
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:27,460
I'd end up raising a BL flag.

328
00:19:41,830 --> 00:19:43,220
My work experience.

329
00:19:44,540 --> 00:19:46,120
I'm so glad I chose this place.

330
00:19:55,280 --> 00:19:56,350
Oh! You haven't paid!

331
00:20:23,580 --> 00:20:25,940
I accidentally raised another flag.

332
00:20:35,680 --> 00:20:36,680
Oh.

333
00:20:37,330 --> 00:20:38,830
Sweet, I won.

334
00:20:40,600 --> 00:20:42,070
My work experience.

335
00:20:43,280 --> 00:20:44,870
I'm so glad I chose this place.

336
00:20:48,070 --> 00:20:50,370
Can I even go back for it now?

337
00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:58,000
Bro, what's up?

338
00:21:05,990 --> 00:21:06,990
Oh.

339
00:21:07,350 --> 00:21:08,550
You won something.

340
00:21:09,410 --> 00:21:10,810
Give it here.

341
00:21:11,070 --> 00:21:12,920
No way, it's mine.

342
00:21:13,760 --> 00:21:15,270
Why not?

343
00:21:16,180 --> 00:21:17,830
It's not like you're gonna use it.

344
00:21:28,410 --> 00:21:29,410
That's not it.

345
00:21:29,620 --> 00:21:31,310
He won't be there next week.

346
00:21:31,310 --> 00:21:32,830
I'll go redeem it then.

347
00:21:34,020 --> 00:21:35,510
What are you talking about?

348
00:21:35,910 --> 00:21:36,910
Nothing.

349
00:21:41,120 --> 00:21:43,210
Hey, don't hide it.

350
00:21:43,520 --> 00:21:44,520
Give it to me.

351
00:21:44,590 --> 00:21:45,200
No way.

352
00:21:45,240 --> 00:21:47,020
I said give it to me!

353
00:21:47,690 --> 00:21:48,110
Man.

354
00:21:48,110 --> 00:21:50,930
I can't believe I raised a flag in a place like this.

355
00:21:51,320 --> 00:21:54,320
I'll have to be more careful from now on.

356
00:21:55,040 --> 00:21:56,040
Later.

